The paper presents a new self-attention based graph neural network for hypergraphs, which is applicable to various learning tasks. The paper also provides extensive evaluations on multiple datasets, including genomics datasets. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
